Project too build a authentication web-service and apply authentication protocols.

Run as:
./index.js [ -t|--auth-time AUTH_TIME ] [ -d|--ssl-dir SSL_DIR ] PORT
where,
-t | --auth-time The time in seconds before an authentication token times
out. If not specified, the value=300 seconds.
-d | --ssl-dir The path to the directory containing SSL credential key.pem and cert.pem. If not specified, the value should default to the directory from which the server was started.

Services:
1. PUT /users/ID?pw=PASSWORD
2. PUT /users/ID/auth
3. GET /users/ID